map p openPaste
map P openPasteTab
" search
map / openSearchBar
map ? openSearchBarReverse
map zz centerMatchH
map n nextSearchResult
map N previousSearchResult
map [[ nextMatchPattern
map ]] previousMatchPattern
map <F4> clearSearchHighlight
" visual
map v toggleVisualMode
map V toggleVisualLineMode
" marks
map m<*> setMark
map '<*> goToMark
" misceallaneous
map % hideDownloadsShelf
map $ cancelWebRequests
